{"tid":938330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果日本分裂成 2 個國家再內戰，東日本定係西日本會贏？","createTime":"2018-12-12T08:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T06:37:58.000Z","uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"554b954bd010617d71567d6cc157b54819a10eb3","tid":938330,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdSPYpk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdSPYpk.png&h=6733291d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以縣地圖做分割<br />\n新瀉、長野、靜岡開始就歸東日本所有<br />\n咁東西日本從軍事、人口、糧食、補給、地利、綜合國力等考慮<br />\n似乎都仲係東日本會贏吧？<br />\n當然撇除沖繩美軍介入呢個可能先&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"051e28e808dbcb84afba67c686fa270585d2da17","tid":938330,"uid":195364,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"以前咪打過囉 無聊"},{"pid":"3a3cdfe6985e98ae52c63427ed92e3ba3f372e29","tid":938330,"uid":51720,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:34:42.000Z","msg":"JR 做緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b5cb419a2ac87d4596e2d5148d76e1cd6254c5","tid":938330,"uid":46849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"051e28e808dbcb84afba67c686fa270585d2da17","tid":938330,"uid":195364,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"以前咪打過囉 無聊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:37:01.000Z","msg":"幾耐以前？"},{"pid":"099cb1783503935cf475485fd36830bfe4e1e71e","tid":938330,"uid":206080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55b5cb419a2ac87d4596e2d5148d76e1cd6254c5","tid":938330,"uid":46849,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"051e28e808dbcb84afba67c686fa270585d2da17","tid":938330,"uid":195364,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:30:51.000Z","msg":"以前咪打過囉 無聊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:37:01.000Z","msg":"幾耐以前？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"東軍 西軍？"},{"pid":"82df2ec